### Health check
GET http://localhost:8002/test

### Listar todos los clientes
GET http://localhost:8002/clientes

### Obtener cliente por ID
GET http://localhost:8002/clientes/1

### Crear cliente
POST http://localhost:8002/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Carlos Mendoza",
    "telefono": "310-555-0101",
    "correo": "carlos@ejemplo.com",
    "numero_licencia": "LIC-001"
}

### Actualizar cliente
PUT http://localhost:8002/clientes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "telefono": "310-999-0000"
}

### Eliminar cliente
DELETE http://localhost:8002/clientes/1
